-= Kitchen =-

You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a fridge. The fridge is empty, what a horrible day! You make out a closed oven nearby. You can make out a table. The table is massive. On the table you can see a cookbook and a knife. Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a counter. But the thing is empty, unfortunately. You can see a stove. But there isn't a thing on it. Aw, here you were, all excited for there to be things on it!
